io.htm |title=Bio of Edison Denisov |publisher=Personal.umich.edu |date= |accessdate=2012-10-28}}</ref>\n* Sonata for Alto Saxophone and Piano, Op. 29 (1970)\u2014[[Robert Muczynski]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pytheasmusic.org/muczynski.html |title=Robert Muczynski at Pytheas ~ Contemporary, Modern, New, Non-Pop Art Music Composers, Ensembles & Resources |publisher=Pytheasmusic.org |date= |accessdate=2012-10-28}}</ref>\n* ''Variations on a Dorian Theme'' for alto saxophone and piano (1972)\u2014[[Gordon Jacob]]\n* ''Four Moods for Alto Saxophone and Piano'' (1975)\u2014[[Phil Woods]]\n* Sonata for Alto Saxophone and Piano'' (1979)\u2014[[John Worley]]\n* ''Albanian Summer (1980)\u2014[[Dave Smith (composer)|Dave Smith]]\n* Divertimento (1982)\u2014[[Charles Wuorinen]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Egge, Mark N |url=http://etd.ohiolink.edu/view.cgi?bgsu1130784707 |title=OhioLINK ETD: Egge, Mark |publisher=Etd.ohiolink.edu |date= |accessdate=2012-10-28}}</ref>\n* ''Peque\u00f1a Czarda'' (1982)\u2014[[Pedro Iturralde]]\n*''Picnic on the Marne'' (1983)\u2014[[Ned Rorem]]\n* Sonata for Alto Saxophone and Piano (1984) [[David Diamond (composer)|David Diamond]]\n* ''Poem'' for Alto Saxophone and Piano(1986)\u2014[[Anders Eliasson]]\n* ''Whirled Series'' (1987)\u2014[[Milton Babbitt]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Andrew |url=http://fauxmat.wordpress.com/2011/01/31/goodnight-milton/ |title=Goodnight Milton \u00ab Fauxmat |publisher=Fauxmat.wordpress.com |date=2011-04-25 |accessdate=2012-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seenandheard-international.com/2011/11/10/multiple-modernisms-bynew-york%E2%80%99s-spunky-counterinduction/ |title=\"Multiple Modernisms\" by New York's spunky counter)induction |publisher=Seen and Heard International |date= |accessdate=2012-10-28}}</ref>\n* ''Keening'' for Alto saxophone and Piano (1987)\u2014[[Michael Berkeley, Baron Berkeley of Knighton|Michael Berkeley]]\n* ''Light of Sothis'' (1987)\u2014Amy Quate\n* Sonata for Alto Saxophone and Piano (1